<p><blockquote>The Mahindra XUV300 is a subcompact crossover SUV produced by the Indian automaker Mahindra & Mahindra. It is based on the X100 platform of Bolero Neo. Mahindra slotted it in the segment along with their Bolero Neo (formerly called the TUV300). It is currently sold as the XUV400 electric car only.</blockquote></p>

