<h2>Mahindra Thar Roxx:</h2>
<img src="https://cdni.autocarindia.com/Utils/ImageResizerV2.ashx?n=https://cms.haymarketindia.net/model/uploads/modelimages/Mahindra-Thar-Roxx-120820241519.jpg" height="400">


<p>The Mahindra Thar Roxx SUV offers great space, features, and value. Its more comfortable and family-oriented package than the standard three-door version. It still maintains its sibling's go-anywhere and do-anything persona with greater practicality.<blockquote > It is offered with 2.0-litre petrol and 2.2-litre diesel engines and both 4WD and 2WD configurations.</blockquote></p>
